59+00', '2025-09-22 11:39:43.559+00'),
(7, 'Can I Request To Switch Trading Platforms For The 2-Step Plus Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "You are allowed to switch between offered Trading Platforms for accounts where no trade is placed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "If a trade is placed, you can request to switch after you reach the next phase, or if it is a Funded Account you can request to switch after full payout is requested and the account is back at Initial Balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'can-i-request-to-switch-trading-platforms-for-the-2-step-plus-accounts', 4, 7, 't', 'f', 'Can I Request To Switch Trading Platforms For The 2-Step Plus Accounts?', 'You are allowed to switch between offered Trading Platforms for accounts where no trade is placed.If a trade is placed, you can request to switch after...', '2025-09-22 11:39:44.077+00', '2025-09-22 11:39:44.077+00'),
(8, 'What Are The Requirements To Merge My 2-Step Plus (Funded) Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2-Step Plus accounts are eligible for merging as long as they are at the initial balance. This applies whether the accounts have not been traded or have returned to the initial balance following a withdrawal request.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'what-are-the-requirements-to-merge-my-2-step-plus-funded-accounts', 4, 8, 't', 'f', 'What Are The Requirements To Merge My 2-Step Plus (Funded) Accounts?', '2-Step Plus accounts are eligible for merging as long as they are at the initial balance. This applies whether the accounts have not been traded or have...', '2025-09-22 11:39:45.564+00', '2025-09-22 11:39:45.564+00'),
(9, 'Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 2-Step Plus Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For 2-Step Plus accounts, there’s no consistency rule in the Evaluation Phase. The consistency rule applies only to the Funded Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Why this Rule?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets’ Consistency Rule promotes steady profit growth and helps traders avoid emotional trading.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Important Details About the Consistency Rule For 2-Step Plus Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Evaluation Phase; there is no consistency rule requirement.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Funded Phase; you should not have made more than 45% of the total profit in one day.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If a single day’s profit is more than 45% of your total profit in the Funded Phase, you have to continue trading until there isn’t a day with more than the above said maximum.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "When is the Consistency Rule Required?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "For 2-Step Plus accounts, it applies only in the Funded Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Calculation", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "[Best Day % of Total Profit] = [Best Day Profit] ÷ [Overall Profit] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit means the highest single day profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Single Day’s Profit = Balance at 5pm EST Today – Balance at 5pm EST Yesterday", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example (2-Step Plus Account – Funded Phase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "If you made a total profit of $10,000 in the Funded Phase,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "To be eligible for withdrawal, there should not have been a single day with more than 45% of $10,000 (= $4,500).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If there is a single day with more than 45% of total profit, then you have to keep on trading until the best day profit is less than 45% of the total profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-there-a-rule-regarding-consistency-for-2-step-plus-accounts', 4, 9, 't', 'f', 'Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 2-Step Plus Accounts?', 'For 2-Step Plus accounts, there’s no consistency rule in the Evaluation Phase. The consistency rule applies only to the Funded Phase. Why this Rule?Fund...', '2025-09-22 11:39:46.01+00', '2025-09-22 11:39:46.01+00'),
