(109, 'Are There Any Limitations On Certain Trading Practices at Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At Funded Trader Markets, we empower traders to choose their trading styles and strategies without restrictions. However, it is crucial to follow our guidelines and avoid activities that exploit our", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "systems or violate fair trading practices. The following actions are strictly prohibited:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Using Manipulative Software or Techniques", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Employing software, AI, ultra-high-speed techniques, or mass data entry methods that manipulate or unfairly advantage your use of our systems is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Non-Standard Trading Practices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in trading practices that deviate from typical forex or financial market trading, or that could cause financial or other harm to the provider.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Using External or Slow Data Feeds", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Executing trades with external or slow data feeds.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Exploiting Service Errors", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Using trading strategies that take advantage of errors in our services, such as price display errors or delayed updates.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipulative Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in manipulative trades, such as entering simultaneous opposite positions, either individually or in collaboration with others.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging Across Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Hedging between accounts with other evaluation firms similar to Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Management Services", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All accounts in our challenges must be traded exclusively by the account owner once a phase is completed. Any deviation from this rule will be considered a violation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Additionally, only one trader per household and IP address is allowed. Breaching this rule will result in the termination of all accounts involved.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Prohibited Trading Practices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Group Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Group trading and copying trades from others, as well as coordinating and reverse trading with others, are not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "High-Frequency Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in high-frequency trading, which involves trading large volumes of positions at very high speeds, is prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "News Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Rapidly opening and closing multiple positions within seconds around high-impact news releases (e.g., FOMC, NFP, CPI) to exploit market feeds is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Arbitrage Trading: Any form of arbitrage trading, including reverse and latency arbitrage, is strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Multi-Account Reverse Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Reverse trading across multiple accounts, especially around events like FOMC, where you hedge positions across different evaluation firms, is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tick Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Scalping in ticks, which involves opening and closing large position sizes in milliseconds, is prohibited as it cannot be mirrored live.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Internal Reverse Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in reverse trading within Funded Trader Market’s internal accounts is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Copying Trades", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Group Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Coordinating opposing positions across one or multiple evaluation firms to manipulate risk is strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Management Services", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Purchasing or providing account management services or using evaluation firm passing services is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Sharing", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Sharing account information or allowing someone else to pass an account on your behalf will result in account termination.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Mirroring Trades", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": It is not allowed to mirror trades from another trader or group of traders across multiple accounts.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Note", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": If any trader is found engaging in any of the prohibited practices, we reserve the right to close the account and forfeit any associated payout without a refund.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'are-there-any-limitations-on-certain-trading-practices-at-funded-trader-markets', 10, 11, 't', 'f', 'Are There Any Limitations On Certain Trading Practices at Funded Trader Markets?', 'At Funded Trader Markets, we empower traders to choose their trading styles and strategies without restrictions. However, it is crucial to follow our gu...', '2025-09-22 11:40:47.097+00', '2025-09-22 11:40:47.097+00'),
(110, 'Am I Allowed To Use A Trade Copier?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets permits the use of trade copiers in all our programs, you are also allowed to copy trades from your account at another evaluation firm, retail broker, or any external/internal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "source, as long as the trades are originally yours.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Trade copiers are permitted exclusively between Evaluation accounts or between Simulated Funded accounts. Copying trades from an Evaluation account to a Simulated Funded account is", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Copying trades from other sources is not allowed. This includes:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Copying trades from other traders", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Using trade signals", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Deploying the same trading bot as another trader at Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Non-compliance with these rules will lead to the termination of your account.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": null}], "direction": null}}', 'am-i-allowed-to-use-a-trade-copier', 10, 12, 't', 'f', 'Am I Allowed To Use A Trade Copier?', 'Funded Trader Markets permits the use of trade copiers in all our programs, you are also allowed to copy trades from your account at another evaluation...', '2025-09-22 11:40:47.59+00', '2025-09-22 11:40:47.59+00'),
(111, 'Is the Cryptocurrency Market Available To Trade During The Weekend?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Yes, Cryptocurrencies are enabled and available for trading over the weekend on all of the trading platforms offered.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-the-cryptocurrency-market-available-to-trade-during-the-weekend', 10, 13, 't', 'f', 'Is the Cryptocurrency Market Available To Trade During The Weekend?', 'Yes, Cryptocurrencies are enabled and available for trading over the weekend on all of the trading platforms offered.', '2025-09-22 11:40:49.459+00', '2025-09-22 11:40:49.459+00'),
(112, 'Am I Allowed To Hedge At Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In our programs, hedging is permitted when conducted within the confines of a single account. However, hedging across separate accounts, termed opposite account hedging, is prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Allowed: Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Executing the following actions within the same account (Account 1):", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Buying EURUSD (Account 1)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Selling EURUSD (Account 1)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Not Allowed: Opposite Account Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Performing the following actions across distinct accounts (Account 1 and Account 2):", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Buying GBPUSD in one account (Account 1)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Selling GBPUSD in another account (Account 2)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the example above, GBPUSD buy in Account 1 and sell in Account 2 ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "must not overlap", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " at any given point in time.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "A violation of this restriction during the challenge phase on any of our accounts will lead to an upgrade denial and on any of our simulated funded or instant funded account will lead to a total payout rejection alongside contract termination on all affected accounts.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Not Allowed: Overnight", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 